- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper presents formalisation in a proof assistant system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the Gauss-Jordan algorithm and its applications. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the performance and correctness of the generated programs.
